{"tid":1079641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"脫北者組織闖入北韓駐西班牙使館　據報十人涉案","createTime":"2019-03-27T05:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T05:44:21.000Z","uid":8543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"29c6ea5b950df11d2569ebaf7bc3fb787f80ca0a","tid":1079641,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:34:23.000Z","msg":"一個支持脫北者的組織「自由朝鮮」承認，上月闖入北韓駐西班牙大使館。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述西班牙法院的文件報道，當日有10人闖入使館，分別為南韓、美國和墨西哥裔，搶去電腦、硬碟及USB儲存器等，其中3人將一名大使館職員押往地下室，游說對方變節，有成員事後潛逃到美國，法院將會提出引渡要求。其中1人在事發數日後，曾與美國聯邦調查局接觸，聲稱與聯邦調查局共享情報。美國國務院副發言人表示，事件與美國政府無關。<br />\n<br />\n「自由朝鮮」日前在網站發布片段，看到有男子闖入相信是大使館的辦公室，將掛在牆上已故北韓領袖金日成及金正日的畫像掟落地，玻璃碎片四濺。組織表示，行動不是襲擊，只是對北韓大使館內緊急狀況的應對，並沒有打劫，亦沒有使用武器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1449860_1_L_20190327105017.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1449860_1_L_20190327105017.jpg&h=2109ae5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1449860.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1449860.htm&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5Wa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=ad097acf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1449860.htm&h=12fb456e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1449860.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4195f8d632b89dd9e80b0eb0fb1603e90fe2140b","tid":1079641,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.cheollimacivildefense.org/static/images/logo2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cheollimacivildefense.org%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Flogo2.png&h=2fe79b95&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}